{"tid":1648021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭深夜發帖挑機：你班廢柴下星期三阻到我入立法會咪試下阻囉","createTime":"2019-10-12T04:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:44:50.000Z","uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd94993533e5b8e687c05e355d97dac9c3d4f01f","tid":1648021,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/carrielam.hksar/photos/a.745574808955421/1288060914706805/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcarrielam.hksar%2Fphotos%2Fa.745574808955421%2F1288060914706805%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=b2dfb3d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/carrielam.hksar/photos/a.745574808955421/1288060914706805/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">往時《施政報告》要做足保密功夫，同事對報告嘅內容都要守口如瓶。今年考慮到情況特殊，各位局長喺我發表《施政報告》前可以率先公布惠民嘅新措施，已經講咗比市民聽嘅有：<br />\n<br />\n＋ 動用105億元幫助舊樓業主維修樓宇、電梯同埋加強消防設備；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 加強兒童體能智力測驗中心服務，同埋喺學校更好支援有自閉症嘅學生；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 喺天水圍天秀路公園旁邊嘅空地設立臨時街市，最快出年年尾完工啟用；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 為精英運動員提供更多資助，備戰明年東京奧運，增加各體育總會嘅資助培養年輕運動員，同埋支持體育學院建新大樓。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我下個禮拜三發表嘅《施政報告》會公布更多措施，<span style=\"color: red;\">希望能夠順利入到立法會大樓啦</span>。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7445cc69bdd7e648b9e3d76df9e4f72066099b8","tid":1648021,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c656b926986f7c5d33c167cad229ac7bbfb3d4","tid":1648021,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"［核彈行動］令警察家變！針對警妻開闢新文宣線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data